query:
SELECT 
  d.id,
  d.numeroCi,
  COUNT(dt.id) as qtd_turmas_vinculadas
FROM despesas_v2 d
LEFT JOIN despesas_v2_turmas dt ON dt.despesaId = d.id
GROUP BY d.id, d.numeroCi
ORDER BY d.numeroCi DESC
LIMIT 10;
